<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row-fluid">

    <div class="span12">
      <h1>Updates to site!</h1>
      <div class="well">
        
        <p>I've just updated the site with some new features and improvements.</p>

        <h2>Discussion forum interface improved.</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>When you reply to a post, you can now see the original post on the same page</li>
          <li>Added background wells to improve the UI</li>
